OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FA council has apologised for failing
OL,7,Fto tell parents a man convicted of
OL,8,Fchild sex offences had been working
OL,9,Fwithin children's services.
OL,11,FMark Campbell was caught in an
OL,12,Fundercover police sting operation
OL,13,Fwhile he believed he was chatting to a
OL,14,F13-year-old girl online. He also had a
OL,15,Fcollection of indecent images of
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
