OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FThe 52-year-old, of Telford Close,
OL,7,FBackworth, North Tyneside, was jailed
OL,8,Ffor 18 months after pleading guilty to
OL,9,Fattempting to incite a girl aged 13-15
OL,10,Fto engage in sexual activity and
OL,11,Fattempting to engage in sexual
OL,12,Fcommunication with a child. He also
OL,13,Fadmitted three counts of possessing
OL,14,Findecent images of children.
OL,16,FCampbell was employed by North
OL,17,FTyneside Council in children's
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FIt is understood that Campbell was
OL,7,Fsuspended by the local authority once
OL,8,Fthe allegations came to light and he
OL,9,Fhas since been dismissed.
OL,11,FIn a statement to the Local Democracy
OL,12,FReporting Service, Rebecca Wall,
OL,13,FDirector of Children's Services at
OL,14,FNorth Tyneside Council, said: "We are
OL,15,Fsorry that some families learned about
OL,16,Fthis matter online rather than hearing
OL,17,Ffrom us directly. We completely
OL,18,Funderstand the worry, upset, and
OL,19,Ffrustration this may have caused, and
OL,20,Fwe would like to offer our sincere
OL,21,Fapologies.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,F"We know that parents place immense
OL,7,Ftrust in us, and we recognise how
OL,8,Funsettling this situation will be for
OL,9,Fmany. Our ambition is always to be as
OL,10,Fopen and transparent as possible.
OL,11,FHowever, we have to work with the
OL,12,Flegal and court processes and while
OL,13,Fthese processes are ongoing there are
OL,14,Flegal limitations on what can be
OL,15,Fshared.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,F"As soon as we became aware of the
OL,7,Foutcome, we took immediate steps to
OL,8,Fcontact families and provide
OL,9,Freassurance and support. We remain
OL,10,Fcommitted to listening to families'
OL,11,Fconcerns and responding to any
OL,12,Fquestions they may have."
OL,14,FNewcastle Crown Court heard last week
OL,15,Fhow Campbell had asked to see a
OL,16,Fpicture of who he believed to be a 13-
OL,17,Fyear-old girl's private parts and he
OL,18,Fsent her an image of his penis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FHe told her he didn't care about their
OL,7,Fage difference but they would have to
OL,8,Fbe "discreet and careful".
OL,10,FTwo mobile phones were seized by
OL,11,Fpolice when they attended his address
OL,12,Fand indecent images of children aged
OL,13,Fbetween six months and 10 years were
OL,14,Flater discovered.
OL,16,FSeven category A images ` the most
OL,17,Fserious ` as well as one category B
OL,18,Fimage and five category C images were
OL,19,Ffound on the devices.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
