OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FJane Foley, defending, told the court:
OL,7,F"He is now 52 so it's quite something
OL,8,Fthat he's now in court having lost his
OL,9,Fgood character in these circumstances.
OL,10,FThe defendant was a lonely individual
OL,11,Fsuffering with mental health
OL,12,Fdifficulties at the time.
OL,14,F"He's suffered from post-traumatic
OL,15,Fstress disorder following his time in
OL,16,Fthe Army. He has counselling sessions
OL,17,Ffrom a veterans charity."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
