PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784290698
OL,3,CMan convicted of child sex offences
OL,4,Cworked in children's services
OL,6,FRecorder Matthew Rose sentenced
OL,7,FCampbell, who left the armed forces in
OL,8,F1993, to 18 months in prison. He also
OL,9,Fimposed a sexual harm prevention order
OL,10,Fand notification requirements for 10
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
